Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.60,02_rch,#1,0,0,0,,{\frz45\frx0\fry0\1c&H3f4c6f\3c&H645037\fs38\bord0\shad0\b0\move(1270.667,670.667,994.667,386.667,0,620)}我還只是一個
